entries.title_d: Onslaught: Survive the Kimogila ambush. They planned on some revenge after you defeated one of their leaders. Thwart their revenge and defeat your ambushers!
entries.title: Dathomir System: Survive the Kimogila Ambush
entries.complete: \#pcontrast2 Station Command: Well done. We didn't learn of their planned ambush until it was too late.
